happening from the morning.

6
00:00:51,350 --> 00:00:52,780
What's with you?

7
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:55,430
You open the bathroom
door then tell me to lock it.

8
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:57,320
Why should I get yelled at?

9
00:00:57,750 --> 00:00:59,680
You should be the
one to apologize.

10
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:01,580
Will you lock the door
when you're using it?

11
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:03,090
Knock first before
you come in.

12
00:01:03,090 --> 00:01:05,630
You came into my room
without knocking first.

13
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:08,000
How am I supposed
to knock on this?

14
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,630
Don't do to others what you
don't want done to you. Stupid.

15
00:01:11,530 --> 00:01:13,270
Now I'm upset!

16
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:17,270
Will you be a little
more considerate here?

17
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:18,800
What's with all these
photos anyway?

18
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,270
I'm at a sensitive age!

19
00:01:20,610 --> 00:01:22,860
These are so disgusting!
Don't leave them here!

20
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:24,750
They're for my job.

21
00:01:26,510 --> 00:01:29,250
If they're so precious,
store them away somewhere!

22
00:01:30,950 --> 00:01:33,150
- What?
- What is it?

23
00:01:36,690 --> 00:01:38,460
Aren't you conscious?

24
00:01:38,930 --> 00:01:41,900
Isn't this making
you conscious?

25
00:01:42,630 --> 00:01:44,570
Just clear them away!

26
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:46,840
Then do something
about that.

27
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,140
"That"?

28
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:51,040
Anybody can see that
we have one too many.

29
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:55,010
That's what Mama
and I used.

30
00:01:55,010 --> 00:01:56,720
It's using electricity.

31
00:01:57,720 --> 00:02:00,810
As I told you before,
I have no money.

32
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,190
Don't say it so proudly.

33
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:05,790
But I gave you the money
to go to prep school.

34
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:08,000
Don't talk big.

35
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,420
But I have every right
to talk big.

36
00:02:13,330 --> 00:02:17,200
Marimo, it's hard
to earn a living.

37
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:20,600
We can't be wasteful.

38
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,510
You said these photos
are disgusting.

39
00:02:24,510 --> 00:02:26,710
But I'm earning
a living with it.

40
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:31,180
Will you give it some
serious thought here?

41
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:42,100
Say...

42
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:50,500
So you didn't go
to prep school.

43
00:02:53,970 --> 00:02:55,790
Were you planning
to pocket it?

44
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:57,900
Don't accuse me of that!

45
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,540
I raised the money to
send you to prep school!

46
00:02:59,540 --> 00:03:01,710
- 300,000 yen, too!
- How can I possibly go?

47
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,840
Why not?

48
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,280
If you keep harping
about how poor you are,

49
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,710
